OBCQL_WIDGET_QUERY.HQL: select distinct cw.id as id,cf.filename as BOQFileName,cw.documentno as DocumentNo,bp.name as BusinessPartner,pr.name as Project ,cf.fileView as FileView from DTZK_Boqimportdata boq left join boq.contractboqfile cf left join cf.contractwork cw left join cw.bpartner bp left join cw.project pr where upper(boq.data) LIKE upper((:Data)) and cw.id IS NOT NULL
